The paper discusses an algorithm for performing efficient context-sensitive analysis incrementally on modular partitions of programs, which is relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the use of fixpoint algorithms, which is relevant to logic in computer science (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of the algorithm, which is relevant to computer security (cs.CR) and systems and control (cs.SY).
